---
layout: 'base'
title: 'Projects'
---

<h1 class="title">Projects</h1>

<p class="subtitle mb-16">
  The open source projects that I have built myself and some that I've contributed to over the years.
</p>

<div class="projects-grid" id="projects">
  {% asyncEach project in projects.projects %}
    {% include "projectCard.njk" %}
  {% endeach %}
</div>

<h2 class="projects-page" id="contributions">Notable Contributions</h2>
<div class="projects-grid">
  {% asyncEach project in projects.contributions %}
    {% include "projectCard.njk" %}
  {% endeach %}
</div>

<h2 class="projects-page" id="github">Contributions on GitHub</h2>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-3 mb-12">
  {% asyncEach repo in contributions %}
  <div class="flex gap-x-2 justify-between">
    <a rel="noreferrer" class="font-semibold text-sm break-all underline-offset-2 hover:underline" href="{{ repo.url }}">
      <span class="text-fg-dimmed">{{ repo.nameWithOwner.split('/')[0] }}/</span><span>{{ repo.nameWithOwner.split('/')[1] }}</span>
    </a>
    <div class="flex gap-x-1 items-center text-fg-dimmed">
      {% icon 'lucide:star', class='block w-3 h-3 fill-current stroke-none' %}
      <span class="text-xs font-medium">{{ repo.stargazers.totalCount | shortCount }}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endeach %}
</div>

<h2 class="projects-page" id="minecraft">Minecraft Mods</h2>
<div class="projects-grid">
  {% asyncEach project in projects.mods %}
    {% include "projectCard.njk" %}
  {% endeach %}
</div>

<h2 class="projects-page" id="archived">Archived Projects</h2>
<div class="projects-grid">
